{"tid":868804,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多叫人領養代替購買既人，自己都係養緊名種貓狗？","createTime":"2018-10-19T20:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T02:30:01.000Z","uid":72939,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"903e1bb4f38c22765aeb44b340923c07cc0beba6","tid":868804,"uid":72939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"fb d貓狗group見唔少，真係咁多名種貓狗可以領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfeecc58eb3d44e8bb9fe4362e245a6c24f56bd","tid":868804,"uid":167067,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:05:55.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦<br />\n有口話人無口話自己<br />\n吹咩"},{"pid":"e9281c1e97f7732807d32fa31bcad61ea5bb019b","tid":868804,"uid":5220,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T21:02:19.000Z","msg":"唔偽善都唔會做動物撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5480b335b12d8c3dd761eac9208b6e0cee6ca304","tid":868804,"uid":16256,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"一早就問過啦 偽善 <br />\n有人問點先領養到名種貓 <br />\n竟然有人答冇辦法買啦 我個隻朋友送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70574a25ce498306d94457bfda1c116abe7ff44","tid":868804,"uid":76516,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"我隻摺耳人地送既 仲有隻黃貓係街執 無買過 都無去領養過"},{"pid":"c3dcc6c9a6b46c8f71cfb83f170ec5e93476bf20","tid":868804,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"係呀 吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8d556a7af752d758d85392c267b13927d3b38e","tid":868804,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"被你發現咗添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7946b655eb6a56a681f35f19ef41fa8bcbae4eb2","tid":868804,"uid":59895,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"可遇不可求，不過領養得既通常都係有啲問題。 <br />\n<br />\n我屋企隻牧羊都係領養返嚟，d義工話係因為佢個鼻太長（個樣唔夠正宗），所以冇寵物店肯要。繁殖場又賣唔出又唔攞得嚟繁殖， 所以一直用個連企起身都唔夠位既細籠養住佢， 直到佢歲幾先畀義工救番佢出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n當我領養佢返黎嘅時候，成隻瘦到見骨，d毛又一撻撻。 四隻腳因為關籠關得太耐， 對腳冇力行路趷下趷下， 同其他狗玩個陣會突然間隻腳冇力成隻碌低。"},{"pid":"7eacca3946b8eb2f85f286849aab52f7ffc7457d","tid":868804,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"果隻摺耳貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401d6b28757a565e1a455b07ed03e268acd6e2d8","tid":868804,"uid":166785,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:01:37.000Z","msg":"口號黎 唔洗太認真"},{"pid":"7fc8a26cc8169bab62dd04471896c6ddde893c08","tid":868804,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"916c26e16f644ed5b1249db8f006cab2232c13e9","tid":868804,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"401d6b28757a565e1a455b07ed03e268acd6e2d8","tid":868804,"uid":166785,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:01:37.000Z","msg":"口號黎 唔洗太認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"講完有型D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad7cc325ca1037721c7345dc8d9418a2081f091","tid":868804,"uid":77201,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb91680eaa3a88b730ef20b541eb0c3aa55b907","tid":868804,"uid":27221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"大把<br />\n養幾隻摺耳貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎啲貓去出書賺錢<br />\n就講自己少不更事唔知摺耳貓有問題 <br />\n又懶係宣傳叫人唔好養摺耳<br />\n又叫人領養 自己一隻都無領養到<br />\n扮撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b7e7d77ee7ce1c85bbcd20bad88ecbed50f4c6","tid":868804,"uid":69763,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T22:22:45.000Z","msg":"其實領養門檻好高<br />\n無乜人真係領養到<br />\n領養唔到又想養米買<br />\n買又唔洗查家宅<br />\n又可以簡隻鐘意嘅<br />\n領養細貓又話愛貓就養成貓<br />\n領養成貓又叫人領養病貓<br />\n都痴痴地"},{"pid":"e3e0fd4a78f8a5269d46b116d9bcb75658272588","tid":868804,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:18:40.000Z","msg":"好多都係領養緊幾隻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過買名種養再出聲果d同海外華人反港獨一樣on9"},{"pid":"324ef818cb99774160eee73f09f55eb5a1379f8b","tid":868804,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:32:32.000Z","msg":"全部領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656d922d4d975d8b8ccb5e017a2515669548751d","tid":868804,"uid":157509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:50:30.000Z","msg":"一隻英短一隻唐貓<br />\n都係領養<br />\n隻英短係係繁殖場唔要<br />\n天生器官有問題最近仲發現有cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b9019f30453bd785d96deea3cdf7a06dc25341","tid":868804,"uid":11774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:55:51.000Z","msg":"其實好多名種到咗咁上下歲數就無人要<br />\n都要人領養㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔一定唐狗/家貓先係領返嚟嘅<br />\n我隻Poodle都用咗好多錢先救返佢條命"},{"pid":"c4815d84b2a283f076a99a88cc3f33c98d38260d","tid":868804,"uid":2839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"咁一定會有d 咁既人, 我識朋友包括自己, 都真係養緊唐貓."},{"pid":"49c6dfb2c5d99eb0b738df20ffbc5d243ac57a15","tid":868804,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"好多人買完名種再同你講領養代替購買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32a9e4cb23b8a1ddc2a5f5d798761ff8555ce1a","tid":868804,"uid":90946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"repl